<h2>The Content Mix That Builds Trust</h2>
<p>Most vet clinics fall into one of 2 traps: posting only promotions (annoying) or posting only cute photos (nice but does not drive appointments). The fix is a balanced content mix.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="Veterinary social media content mix formula" src="/images/blog/vet-social-content-mix.webp" /></p>
